      "title": "Doctors of Badulla General Hospital ride bicycles",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At the Badulla General Hospital, a team of pediatricians, surgeons, oncologists, gynecologists, neurologists, cardiologists, orthopedic surgeons and other doctors are currently on duty on bicycles to alleviate fuel shortages."
